{"tid":2200487,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【苦不堪言】26歲女子擁42L巨胸成困擾　彎腰致脊椎受傷需輪椅代步","createTime":"2020-09-13T04:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T05:24:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a24352540f0161f2d0067ae2f655dbac26d31b5","tid":2200487,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"擁有傲人上圍原來並非人人稱羨，英國26歲女子黛比（Debbie Horton）本身更擁有驚人的42L巨乳，但胸部的重量卻令她數年前在彎腰拾東西時，不幸導致脊椎嚴重損傷。原本熱愛運動的她經歷手術後，現在只能以輪椅代步，目前她希望可籌得7000英鎊善款去進行縮胸手術，減輕胸前的負擔。<br />\n<br />\n手術後後遺症頻生<br />\n據英媒《每日郵報》報道，黛比自學生時期開始，胸部就比其他同儕來得豐滿，成年後罩杯更飆升至42L，逐漸成為龐大負擔。不過，她本身是一名熱愛運動的女生，除了日常會進行健身外，更是一名三項鐵人賽事的運動員。<br />\n<br />\n直至在2016年9月，她在超市工作彎腰拾東西時，背部再也無法支撐她上身的重量，使她背部一震痠痛，當場倒地不起。經送院檢查，發現她患有嚴重脊椎側彎，即使經過手術治療，仍留下嚴重的後遺症。她過去4年來陸續出現椎間盤退化、椎間盤突出、脊椎炎、頸椎前曲、纖維肌痛症等疾病，生活苦不堪言。<br />\n<br />\n未婚夫不離不棄<br />\n病情不僅讓她急速發胖，現在她還必須靠輪椅才能長距離移動，近日更罹患了紅斑性狼瘡。對於自己的情況，黛比曾經向未婚夫指：「如果你想離開，找一個能和你一起過正常、幸福日子的人，也沒關係」，但遭未婚夫斷言拒絕，讓她大嘆：<br />\n&quot;能得到他的支持，真的是很幸運的事！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n事實上，黛比在去年11月已接受了3次脊椎治療手術，但至今她仍然難以行走。加上近日她又被診斷患上「紅斑性狼瘡」，皮膚變得敏感，不能穿戴胸罩。少了胸罩的支撐，使她的負擔越來越重。目前，已為病情散盡家財的黛比發起網上眾籌，希望募得7000英鎊去進行縮胸手術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2751545/42l_thumb_20200913_K_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2751545%2F42l_thumb_20200913_K_1024.jpg&h=38176b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2751545/006_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2751545%2F006_1024.jpg&h=29d28640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2751545/004_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2751545%2F004_1024.jpg&h=498e330b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2751545/003_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2751545%2F003_1024.jpg&h=34fd3553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2751545/005_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2751545%2F005_1024.jpg&h=9418ea8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c207ab852f0a2e65ee5dfa4a2f278ba4770d784","tid":2200487,"uid":317345,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"可以分啲俾港女就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6376a18b343aca42f3cc99688076543e32946bff","tid":2200487,"uid":16041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"本身都肥"},{"pid":"b9d5556a598260f6a0736119f4a00c9c048e4a5b","tid":2200487,"uid":86756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"大過人個頭"},{"pid":"f8963002222af680e391e1f7a80f1494f6b6cec1","tid":2200487,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚野不離不棄<br />\n賴死唔走咋掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9b3bc9eed095c48bd7d67727e09a801911e27d","tid":2200487,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28ba6d194fbeeabcd6c0780d383961ff4b764e86","tid":2200487,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"本身肥 背厚<b